%center
  %h2{:style => "text-decoration:none; color:#58616c;"}
    ="A reminder about your upcoming event"
%div.email-body{ :style => "border-radius: 25px; padding: 20px; border: 2px solid #58616c;" }
  %center
    %h1
      =link_to @event.name, event_url(@rsvp.event, rsvp:@rsvp.hash_key), only_path: false, :style => "text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"
    %h3
      ="Organized by " + @event.owner.display_name  
    %div{:style => "text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"}
      =@event.html_description.html_safe
    %hr{ :style => "border: 0; height: 1px; background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));"}
    %h2{:style => "text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"}
      =@event.display_time_wordy
      %br
      -unless @event.location.blank?
        ="at"
        %br
        =@event.location

    %hr{ :style => "border: 0; height: 1px; background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));"}
    %table
      %tr
        %td
          %a{ :href => event_url(@event, @rsvp.hash_key), only_path: false, :style => "background-color:#fe6333;-moz-border-radius:28px;-webkit-border-radius:28px;border-radius:28px;display:inline-block; cursor:pointer; color:#ffffff; font-family:Arial; font-size:17px; padding:10px 22px; text-decoration:none;"}
            View Event
            
%center
  =link_to "The Sipping Point", root_url, only_path: false, :style => "text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold;color:#58616c;word-spacing:2pt;font-size:20px;"
  %div{ :style => "text-decoration:none;color:#58616c;font-size:14px;"}
    The Sipping Point is the best way to make sure you have a critical mass for your event.When enough people are in, the Sipping Point is reached and the event is on! 
    =link_to "Click here", root_url, only_path: false, :style => "text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold;color:#58616c;"
    to plan your next gathering.
